snippet.title: HITMAN: Trinity Pack - Trailer
snippet.description:
Previously only available to anyone who pre-ordered HITMAN 3 prior to its release in 2021, The Trinity Pack celebrates each game in the World of Assassination trilogy with a total of 9 items. 

The items are comprised of an ICA 19 variant, briefcase and suit in the following colours: Premiere White of HITMAN 1, the Crimson Red of HITMAN 2 and the Ultimate Black of HITMAN 3.
